com.emc.storageos.model.valid

Annotation Type Endpoint


  • @Documented
@Target(value={METHOD,FIELD})
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Endpoint
    An annotation to indicate that a field represents an communication endpoint that can be used to export volumes or file systems. This annotation is mostly used to validate the use input.
